---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Iman Abdul Rahim — Licensed Financial Planner | CFP® | IFP">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-bg"></div>
    <div class="container hero-inner">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <p class="section-label">Licensed Financial Planner · CFP® · IFP</p>
        <h1 class="hero-title">Nak rancang kewangan?<br /><em>Jom buat betul-betul.</em></h1>
        <p class="hero-sub">I tolong Malaysians macam you untuk bina kekayaan, protect apa yang penting, dan plan for the future — dengan nasihat kewangan yang personalised dan tak bias.</p>
        <div class="hero-actions">
          <a href="/planning" class="btn btn--primary">Tengok Financial Planning</a>
          <a href="/fhc" class="btn btn--outline">Financial Health Check — RM350</a>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-trust">
          <span class="trust-badge">CFP® Certified</span>
          <span class="trust-badge">Islamic Financial Planner</span>
          <span class="trust-badge">SC Licensed</span>
          <span class="trust-badge">BNM Licensed</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Services -->
  <section class="section section--alt" id="services">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="section-label">Services</p>
      <h2 class="section-heading">Macam mana I boleh <em>bantu you.</em></h2>
      <p class="section-sub">Dua cara untuk start financial planning journey you — pilih yang sesuai dengan keperluan you.</p>

      <div class="services-grid">
        <a href="/planning" class="service-card card">
          <div class="sc-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z"/><path d="M2 17l10 5 10-5"/><path d="M2 12l10 5 10-5"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="sc-tag">12-Month Engagement</div>
          <h3>Full Financial Planning</h3>
          <p>Engagement setahun yang cover semua aspek kewangan you — cash flow, investments, protection, estate, tax, dan goals-based planning — semua tailored untuk hidup you.</p>
          <span class="sc-link">Baca lagi <span>→</span></span>
        </a>

        <a href="/fhc" class="service-card card">
          <div class="sc-icon sc-icon--gold">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="sc-tag">One-Time Review</div>
          <h3>Financial Health Check</h3>
          <p>One-time review untuk check keadaan kewangan you. Dapat insights yang jelas dan objective, takde product push — you akan tahu apa yang okay, apa yang perlu improve, dan macam mana nak betulkan.</p>
          <div class="sc-price">RM 350</div>
          <span class="sc-link">Book sekarang <span>→</span></span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About -->
  <section class="section" id="about">
    <div class="container about-grid">
      <div class="about-content">
        <p class="section-label">About</p>
        <h2 class="section-heading">Kewangan you deserve<br /><em>nasihat yang betul.</em></h2>
        <p class="about-text">I'm Iman Abdul Rahim — Licensed Financial Planner dengan pengalaman 5 tahun tolong Malaysians macam you take control of duit sendiri.</p>
        <p class="about-text">I licensed dengan Securities Commission Malaysia dan Bank Negara Malaysia, dan I pegang CFP® dan Islamic Financial Planner (IFP) certifications. I terikat dengan ethical codes dan fiduciary standards — maknanya, I kena always act in YOUR best interest.</p>
        <div class="about-creds">
          <div class="cred">
            <span class="cred-title">CFP®</span>
            <span class="cred-org">Certified Financial Planner, FPAM</span>
          </div>
          <div class="cred">
            <span class="cred-title">IFP</span>
            <span class="cred-org">Islamic Financial Planner, IBFIM</span>
          </div>
          <div class="cred">
            <span class="cred-title">HRD Corp</span>
            <span class="cred-org">Accredited Trainer</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="section section--pink" id="faq">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="section-label">FAQ</p>
      <h2 class="section-heading">Soalan <em>lazim.</em></h2>

      <div class="faq-list">
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-q">Financial Planner ni buat apa sebenarnya?</summary>
          <div class="faq-a">
            <p>Licensed Financial Planner tolong individuals dan families buat keputusan kewangan yang informed supaya boleh capai life goals — melalui nasihat yang personalised dan structured.</p>
            <p>Nasihat I always in your best interest, bukan nak push product. I juga tolong dengan implementation dan buat regular reviews supaya you stay on track.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-q">Nasihat ni Shariah compliant ke?</summary>
          <div class="faq-a">
            <p>Yes, memang. I offer Shariah-compliant financial planning, termasuk Islamic investment portfolios, takaful, dan zakat planning. You boleh request supaya seluruh financial plan you Shariah-aligned.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-q">Info I confidential ke?</summary>
          <div class="faq-a">
            <p>Mestilah. I comply dengan PDPA regulations dan jaga confidentiality you dengan ketat. Semua data yang you share disimpan securely dan hanya digunakan untuk planning purposes dengan consent you.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-q">Berapa kos financial planning ni?</summary>
          <div class="faq-a">
            <p>Financial Health Check tu one-time session je, RM 350. Full Financial Planning pulak engagement 12 bulan — fees kita discuss masa initial consultation based on complexity. Jom book free discovery call dulu untuk tahu lebih lanjut.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-q">I baru grad — sesuai ke untuk I?</summary>
          <div class="faq-a">
            <p>Memang sesuai lah! Financial Health Check ni perfect untuk sesiapa yang baru nak start financial journey. You akan dapat clarity tentang where you stand sekarang dan actionable steps untuk move forward dengan yakin.</p>
          </div>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="section cta-section">
    <div class="container cta-inner">
      <h2 class="cta-heading">Jom start plan<br /><em>kewangan you.</em></h2>
      <p class="cta-sub">Kita mula dengan borak-borak dulu. Takde obligation, takde product push — just honest guidance.</p>
      <div class="cta-actions">
        <a href="https://wa.me/60186617981?text=Hi%20Iman%2C%20I'd%20like%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20your%20financial%20planning%20services." target="_blank" class="btn btn--wa">Chat on WhatsApp</a>
        <a href="/fhc" class="btn btn--outline">Book Financial Health Check</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* Hero */
  .hero {
    padding: 10rem 0 6rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: var(--cream);
  }

  .hero-bg {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 70% 20%, var(--pink-soft) 0%, transparent 50%),
                radial-gradient(ellipse at 20% 80%, var(--blush) 0%, transparent 40%);
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  .hero-inner { position: relative; z-index: 1; max-width: 700px; }

  .hero-title {
    font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 5.5vw, 3.8rem);
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
  }

  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.9;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    max-width: 560px;
  }

  .hero-actions { display: flex; gap: 0.8rem; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 2rem; }

  .hero-trust { display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .trust-badge {
    font-size: 0.68rem; padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem; border-radius: 100px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border); color: var(--text-muted); font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  /* Services */
  .services-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1.5rem; margin-top: 2.5rem; }
  .service-card {
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem;
    text-decoration: none; color: inherit;
  }
  .sc-icon {
    width: 56px; height: 56px; border-radius: 16px;
    background: var(--pink); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    color: var(--rose-gold);
  }
  .sc-icon--gold { background: rgba(201,160,122,0.1); color: var(--gold); }
  .sc-tag { font-size: 0.68rem; color: var(--rose-gold); font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .service-card h3 { font-size: 1.3rem; }
  .service-card p { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-secondary); font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.8; flex-grow: 1; }
  .sc-price {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--gold); margin-top: -0.5rem;
  }
  .sc-link {
    font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--rose-gold); font-weight: 600;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.3rem; transition: gap 0.2s;
  }
  .service-card:hover .sc-link { gap: 0.6rem; }

  /* About */
  .about-grid { max-width: 700px; }
  .about-text { font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.9; font-weight: 300; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .about-creds { display: flex; gap: 1.5rem; margin-top: 1.5rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .cred {
    padding: 1rem 1.5rem; background: var(--white); border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
    border-radius: 14px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.2rem;
  }
  .cred-title { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--rose-gold); }
  .cred-org { font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--text-muted); font-weight: 400; }

  /* FAQ */
  .faq-list { max-width: 700px; margin-top: 2rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0; }
  .faq-item {
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 1.2rem 0;
  }
  .faq-q {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text); cursor: pointer; list-style: none; display: flex;
    align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
  }
  .faq-q::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }
  .faq-q::after { content: '+'; font-size: 1.2rem; color: var(--rose-gold); transition: transform 0.2s; }
  details[open] .faq-q::after { content: '−'; }
  .faq-a { padding-top: 0.8rem; }
  .faq-a p { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.8; font-weight: 300; margin-bottom: 0.6rem; }

  /* CTA */
  .cta-section {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--text) 0%, #5a333d 100%);
    text-align: center;
  }
  .cta-inner { max-width: 600px; }
  .cta-heading { font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.4rem); color: var(--pink); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .cta-heading em { color: var(--rose-gold-light); }
  .cta-sub { font-size: 0.95rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); font-weight: 300; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .cta-actions { display: flex; gap: 0.8rem; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero { padding: 8rem 0 4rem; }
    .services-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .hero-actions { flex-direction: column; }
    .hero-actions .btn { text-align: center; }
    .about-creds { flex-direction: column; }
    .cta-actions { flex-direction: column; align-items: center; }
  }
</style>
